actors.name: Institute of Internal Auditors Student Chapter - FEU

message.text:
𝐋𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐮𝐩 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐈𝐀𝐒𝐂-𝐅𝐄𝐔! 💚💙

Think you’ve got what it takes to shine on the court or dominate online? Now’s your chance to represent us in basketball, volleyball, table tennis, badminton, chess, and E-Sports!

The Institute of Internal Auditors Student Chapter-FEU is opening its doors to students who are ready to rise, compete, and leave a mark. Be part of a community that celebrates sportsmanship as much as success. Let’s set new standards together in the Athlete Search 2025!

Registration is now open until the maximum slots are filled.

ATHLETE SEARCH REGISTRATION FORM
 📌 https://bit.ly/AthleteSearch2025RegistrationForm

Step into the arena with Integrity, aim for Excellence, and let the colors Blue and Green shine in every rally, shot, checkmate, and clutch play!

For further inquiries, kindly reach out:
Elgar James Caharian - Vice President

#IAbante

Caption by Elgar James Caharian
Pubmat by Samantha Mascariñas and Elgar James Caharian

message.text:
𝐋𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐮𝐩 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐈𝐀𝐒𝐂-𝐅𝐄𝐔! 💚💙

Think you’ve got what it takes to shine on the court or dominate online? Now’s your chance to represent us in basketball, volleyball, table tennis, badminton, chess, and E-Sports!

The Institute of Internal Auditors Student Chapter-FEU is opening its doors to students who are ready to rise, compete, and leave a mark. Be part of a community that celebrates sportsmanship as much as success. Let’s set new standards together in the Athlete Search 2025!

Registration is now open until the maximum slots are filled.

ATHLETE SEARCH REGISTRATION FORM
 📌 https://bit.ly/AthleteSearch2025RegistrationForm

Step into the arena with Integrity, aim for Excellence, and let the colors Blue and Green shine in every rally, shot, checkmate, and clutch play!

For further inquiries, kindly reach out:
Elgar James Caharian - Vice President

#IAbante

Caption by Elgar James Caharian
Pubmat by Samantha Mascariñas and Elgar James Caharian

𝐋𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐮𝐩 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐠𝐚𝐦𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐈𝐀𝐒𝐂-𝐅𝐄𝐔! 💚💙

Think you’ve got what it takes to shine on the court or dominate online? Now’s your chance to represent us in basketball, volleyball, table tennis, badminton, chess, and E-Sports!

The Institute of Internal Auditors Student Chapter-FEU is opening its doors to students who are ready to rise, compete, and leave a mark. Be part of a community that celebrates sportsmanship as much as success. Let’s set new standards together in the Athlete Search 2025!

Registration is now open until the maximum slots are filled.

ATHLETE SEARCH REGISTRATION FORM
 📌 https://bit.ly/AthleteSearch2025RegistrationForm

Step into the arena with Integrity, aim for Excellence, and let the colors Blue and Green shine in every rally, shot, checkmate, and clutch play!

For further inquiries, kindly reach out:
Elgar James Caharian - Vice President

message.text:
𝑻𝑨𝑴𝑯𝑼𝑵𝑻 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 | 𝑾𝑶𝑹𝑲𝑰𝑵𝑮 𝑪𝑶𝑴𝑴𝑰𝑻𝑻𝑬𝑬 𝑨𝑷𝑷𝑹𝑬𝑪𝑰𝑨𝑻𝑰𝑶𝑵

Narito na nga makalipas ang matagumpay na pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025! ✨ Kilalanin natin ang mga bumubuo ng Working Committee, mula sa iba’t ibang komite na nagsama-sama upang maging posible at matagumpay ang tatlong araw ng TamHunt ngayong taon.

Lubos ang pasasalamat namin sa bawat isa na naging bahagi ng Working Committee, mula sa maagang yugto ng pagpaplano, hanggang sa mismong operasyon ng booth. Mula sa pag-aasikaso ng mga gawain, pagtulong sa mga estudyanteng gustong makilala ang organisasyon, at pagbibigay ng oras at lakas hanggang sa huling araw nitong taunang pagdiriwang. 

Buong puso kaming nagpapasalamat sa mga altruista na tumulong upang maipahayag ang aming mga layunin na nakabatay sa diwa ng paglilingkod. Ito pa lamang ang simula ng ating mga proyekto at adhikain ngayong taon. Abangan pa ang mga susunod na kaganapan ng Tamaraw Volunteers–Manila, at sama-sama nating isabuhay ang #SerbisyongNAGAahon.

𝑰𝑲𝑨, 𝑨𝑲𝑶, 𝑲𝑰𝑻𝑨 𝑨𝑵 𝑻𝑨𝑴𝑽𝑶𝑳!

#AltruismAboveAndBeyond
#ActionOnTheGround

Isinulat nina Cesar Nora III at Jhan Domanais
Inilikha ni Sean Gonzalez

message.text:
𝑻𝑨𝑴𝑯𝑼𝑵𝑻 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 | 𝑾𝑶𝑹𝑲𝑰𝑵𝑮 𝑪𝑶𝑴𝑴𝑰𝑻𝑻𝑬𝑬 𝑨𝑷𝑷𝑹𝑬𝑪𝑰𝑨𝑻𝑰𝑶𝑵

Narito na nga makalipas ang matagumpay na pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025! ✨ Kilalanin natin ang mga bumubuo ng Working Committee, mula sa iba’t ibang komite na nagsama-sama upang maging posible at matagumpay ang tatlong araw ng TamHunt ngayong taon.

Lubos ang pasasalamat namin sa bawat isa na naging bahagi ng Working Committee, mula sa maagang yugto ng pagpaplano, hanggang sa mismong operasyon ng booth. Mula sa pag-aasikaso ng mga gawain, pagtulong sa mga estudyanteng gustong makilala ang organisasyon, at pagbibigay ng oras at lakas hanggang sa huling araw nitong taunang pagdiriwang. 

Buong puso kaming nagpapasalamat sa mga altruista na tumulong upang maipahayag ang aming mga layunin na nakabatay sa diwa ng paglilingkod. Ito pa lamang ang simula ng ating mga proyekto at adhikain ngayong taon. Abangan pa ang mga susunod na kaganapan ng Tamaraw Volunteers–Manila, at sama-sama nating isabuhay ang #SerbisyongNAGAahon.

𝑰𝑲𝑨, 𝑨𝑲𝑶, 𝑲𝑰𝑻𝑨 𝑨𝑵 𝑻𝑨𝑴𝑽𝑶𝑳!

#AltruismAboveAndBeyond
#ActionOnTheGround

Isinulat nina Cesar Nora III at Jhan Domanais
Inilikha ni Sean Gonzalez

Mula sa pag-aasikaso ng mga gawain, pagtulong sa mga estudyanteng gustong makilala ang organisasyon, at pagbibigay ng oras at lakas hanggang sa huling araw nitong taunang pagdiriwang. 

Buong puso kaming nagpapasalamat sa mga altruista na tumulong upang maipahayag ang aming mga layunin na nakabatay sa diwa ng paglilingkod. Ito pa lamang ang simula ng ating mga proyekto at adhikain ngayong taon. Abangan pa ang mga susunod na kaganapan ng Tamaraw Volunteers–Manila, at sama-sama nating isabuhay ang #SerbisyongNAGAahon.
